<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="6Dec1938"><font color="red">6 December 1938</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Richard de la Mere to Paul L&eacute;on): Our printers have just pointed out to us that the final pages &hellip; have already been sent out in proof set up from the second lot of copy that you sent us &hellip; [they] are now going to prepare revised proofs of the last pages &hellip; using that new copy that you sent us, which arrived too late to prevent the earlier copy been set up and I am hoping to send you new proofs quite soon. </div>
